WEBVTT

00:04.671 --> 00:07.731
[Man On TV, Indistinct]

00:07.807 --> 00:11.208
<i>[Water Running]</i>
<i>## [Whistling]</i>

00:13.313 --> 00:16.180
## [Whistling Continues]

00:19.019 --> 00:21.681
Oh!

00:21.755 --> 00:24.451
<i>Hello, Rudy.</i>

00:24.524 --> 00:29.587
Normally, I'd frisk ya to make sure
you're not packin', but in this case
I'll make an exception.

00:29.662 --> 00:31.857
<i>Do you know who I am?</i>

00:31.931 --> 00:34.297
Al Nicoletto.
<i>It's a nice hotel, huh?</i>

00:34.367 --> 00:38.428
I killed a guy here in '95-

00:38.505 --> 00:40.564
'96.

00:40.640 --> 00:42.801
'96. Memories.

00:42.876 --> 00:45.367
I don't have the money.

00:45.445 --> 00:47.970
I swear to God.
<i>Well, then I'll just</i>
<i>let you go, right?</i>

00:48.048 --> 00:50.710
Nobody who swears to God
could possibly be lying.

00:51.718 --> 00:53.652
[Groans]

00:54.888 --> 00:59.154
<i>You and your partner stole $3. 1 million</i>
<i>from our friends in Miami,</i>

00:59.225 --> 01:01.216
more or less.

01:01.294 --> 01:03.387
<i>They don't have</i>
<i>the exact figure yet.</i>
I don't have it.

01:03.463 --> 01:05.954
<i>One hell of an accountant.</i>
Ben took the money.

01:06.032 --> 01:07.966
Ben Gruber, your partner, right?
<i>That's right.</i>

01:08.034 --> 01:10.764
We were supposed to meet up
next week, split the money.

01:10.837 --> 01:14.637
Meet where?
I don't know.
Ben was gonna call.

01:14.707 --> 01:16.971
Where is he?
California.
That's all I know.

01:17.043 --> 01:20.945
The-That postcard over there.

01:25.752 --> 01:28.812
"Sit tight. I'll call next week."

01:30.590 --> 01:33.582
That's all I know. I swear.

01:33.660 --> 01:35.924
I got bad news for you, Rudy.

01:36.996 --> 01:38.930
I believe you.

01:38.998 --> 01:40.989
<i>[Groans]</i>

01:46.206 --> 01:49.334
<i>## [Up-tempo Folk]</i>

01:49.409 --> 01:51.343
<i># It's a jungle out there #</i>

01:51.411 --> 01:55.142
<i># Disorder and confusion</i>
<i>everywhere #</i>

01:56.216 --> 01:58.616
<i># No one seems to care #</i>

01:58.685 --> 02:02.781
<i># Well, I do</i>
<i>Hey, who's in charge here #</i>

02:02.856 --> 02:05.689
<i># It's a jungle out there #</i>

02:05.758 --> 02:09.455
<i># Poison in the very air</i>
<i>we breathe #</i>

02:09.529 --> 02:12.862
<i># Do you know what's in the water</i>
<i>that you drink, well, I do #</i>

02:12.932 --> 02:16.129
<i># And it's amazing #</i>

02:16.202 --> 02:19.365
<i># People think I'm crazy</i>
<i>'cause I worry all the time #</i>

02:19.439 --> 02:21.532
<i># If you paid attention</i>
<i>you'd be worried too #</i>

02:22.976 --> 02:26.742
<i># You better pay attention</i>
<i>or this world we love so much #</i>

02:26.813 --> 02:30.544
<i># Mightjust kill you #</i>

02:30.617 --> 02:33.484
<i># I could be wrong now #</i>

02:33.553 --> 02:35.521
<i># But I don't think so #</i>

02:35.588 --> 02:37.317
<i># 'Cause it's a jungle out there #</i>

02:37.390 --> 02:39.915
<i># It's a jungle out there ##</i>

