37:04.355 --> 37:06.585
<i>Gruber must've needed</i>
<i>more cash,</i>

37:06.657 --> 37:08.989
<i>so he went upstairs to get it.</i>

37:09.060 --> 37:14.521
I went to bed around 10:00.
They were all still playin' the poker.

37:14.599 --> 37:18.126
<i>Monk. We've heard</i>
<i>this part already.</i>

37:18.202 --> 37:21.330
Cappy! Cappy, you made it.

37:21.405 --> 37:25.171
Oh. Oh. How do you do it?

37:25.243 --> 37:30.340
L- l- I love you.

37:30.414 --> 37:32.780
I just- Oh.
[Laughs]

37:32.850 --> 37:36.115
Uh. Uh.
I love you too, Monk.

37:36.187 --> 37:38.883
You just-You just got-

37:38.956 --> 37:40.947
You-

37:42.560 --> 37:45.495
Okay. Let's go sleep it off,
all right?

37:45.563 --> 37:47.929
Thank-Thank-Thanks for the-

37:47.999 --> 37:52.095
What?
Thanks for the-
Look at that.

37:52.169 --> 37:55.036
What's that thing?
[Laughs]

37:55.106 --> 37:57.040
All right, come here.
Come here. Come here.

37:57.108 --> 37:59.099
I'm gonna get me one.
Up to bed.

37:59.176 --> 38:01.167
Oh, w-wait!

38:06.851 --> 38:09.718
<i>See, Gruber never came back.</i>

38:09.787 --> 38:14.281
<i>They got worried</i>
<i>and decided to go upstairs</i>
<i>and check on him.</i>

38:14.358 --> 38:17.657
<i>They found Ben Gruber dead.</i>

38:17.728 --> 38:20.526
<i>He was dead from a heart attack.</i>

38:20.598 --> 38:25.797
<i>And cash</i>- <i>$3. 1 million.</i>

38:25.870 --> 38:29.533
[No Audible Dialogue]
