<i>would be comin'around lookin'for it.</i>

38:29.607 --> 38:32.770
<i>That's the kind of money</i>
<i>people come lookin'for.</i>

38:32.843 --> 38:35.971
<i>What to do? What to do?</i>

38:37.048 --> 38:40.779
