39:02.606 --> 39:06.770
<i>Then they removed the page</i>
<i>with his signature...</i>

39:06.844 --> 39:08.937
<i>from the guest book.</i>

39:09.013 --> 39:12.278
<i>And retook the group photo</i>
<i>without him.</i>

39:12.350 --> 39:16.377
<i>He was gone.</i>
<i>It was like he never existed.</i>

39:16.454 --> 39:18.684
<i>[Shutter Clicks]</i>
<i>Gone like a ghost.</i>

39:19.790 --> 39:23.226
- Did you find the money?
- Not yet.

39:23.294 --> 39:26.092
<i>He says there was a conspiracy,</i>
<i>and we all took the money.</i>

39:26.163 --> 39:30.998
I say this character Gruber
junked his own car,

39:31.068 --> 39:34.094
took the cash,
and hitchhiked to Mexico.

39:34.171 --> 39:37.436
Can you prove
I'm wrong?
Nope.

39:37.508 --> 39:40.136
He's right. Without a body,
we don't have a case.

39:40.211 --> 39:42.145
<i>[Snoring]</i>
Monk?

39:43.447 --> 39:45.381
Monk.

39:45.449 --> 39:47.474
[Snoring Continues]

39:47.551 --> 39:51.612
Okay, um, I guess
you're all free to go.

39:51.689 --> 39:54.886
Lieutenant, take everybody's address.
Make sure it's a valid I.D.

39:54.959 --> 39:58.918
Yes, sir. Uh, if everybody could
just follow me. We're sorry
about the inconvenience.

40:00.364 --> 40:02.298
[Sighs]
What is it?

40:02.366 --> 40:05.699
What is what?
<i>This is their new wine.</i>
<i>They bottle it next door.</i>

40:05.770 --> 40:09.706
