<i>[Natalie]</i>
<i>What's gonna happen to them?</i>

40:49.780 --> 40:53.773
<i>[Stottlemeyer]</i>
<i>They didn't kill anybody,</i>
<i>so they'll probably be home soon.</i>

40:55.586 --> 40:58.646
Uh, he's a real party animal.
[Laughs]

40:58.722 --> 41:03.318
